sequenceDiagram
    %% Sequence Diagram Logout - Rosa & Shalahuddin Style
    participant User
    participant m as m: Main
    participant an as an: Antarmuka
    participant v as v: Validasi

    User->>m: main()
    m->>an: 1: formDashboard()
    User->>an: 2: klik tombol logout
    an->>v: 3: signOut()
    v-->>an: 4: session dihapus
    an-->>User: 5: redirect ke formLogin()